  "aboutCompanyTitle": "Coding Tomorrow, Today.",
  "aboutCompanyBody": "We are a software house specialized in high-performance architectures. We combine the power of Dart/Flutter with the robustness of Java to build digital ecosystems that not only work, but scale. Our mission is to turn complex logic into simplified user experiences, ensuring your technical infrastructure supports growth rather than becoming a bottleneck.",
